            "DescriptionEN": "Sets Blade's current HP to 50% of his Max HP and deals to a single enemy Wind DMG equal to the sum of 48% of his ATK, 120% of his Max HP, and 120% of the total HP he had lost in the current battle. At the same time, deal Wind DMG to adjacent targets equal to 24% of his ATK, 60% of his Max HP, and 60% of the HP he had lost in the current battle.After using his Ultimate, the total HP Blade had lost in the current battle will be reset and re-accumulated. This lost HP value is capped at 90% of his Max HP.",
